    <p class="mb-4">
      I am a 4th-year BSIT student at <strong>Mindoro State University</strong> (Bongabong Campus). I specialize in building secure, transparent, and socially relevant software solutions.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      My expertise spans <strong>Full-Stack Development</strong> and <strong>Blockchain Technology</strong>. I am particularly proud of my work on <em>ProcuChain</em>, where I integrated MultiChain to solve accountability issues in government procurement.
    </p>
    <p>
      I am also a <strong>Hack4Gov 3 Regional Highest Scorer</strong> and National Qualifier, with a deep interest in the diverse domains of cybersecurity and secure system design. I believe in writing code that isn't just functional, but also secure and resilient.
    </p>
